text: 10.25 Mat 9.34, Mak 3.22, Luk 11.15 Anɨb ak tek, bɨ sikul okok kɨli bɨ tisa kɨli ak tek yenɨgabal, anɨb ak tep yɨbɨl agak. Pen bɨ wog gɨñeb okok kɨli bɨawl kɨli ak tek yenɨgabal, anɨb ak tep yɨbɨl agak. Bɨ kal nap nɨb yɨb nop Belsebul10.25 Yɨb Belsebul anɨb ak, Satan yɨb ne olap. apal ak tek, binɨb ne okok kɨlop yɨb tɨmel yɨbɨl ak lɨnɨgabal agak.
